        <abstract> 
<p>Expands on a letter to <hi rend="italic">Nature</hi> concerning the probability of the survival of a new variety in a given species. Differs with [F. Jenkin’s] argument, to which CD had agreed to a greater extent than JB feels it deserved.</p> 
        </abstract>
